        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the slider triggers the associated target’s action method repeatedly, as the user moves the thumb. If "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the slider triggers the associated action method just once, when the user releases the slider’s thumb control to set the final value."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The default value of this property is "
            },
